{"tid":2206898,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–量度紫外線的衣服","createTime":"2020-09-17T20:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T13:26:56.000Z","uid":38861,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"686604accb0d2d805c0900dd8e1122ddcbb3b826","tid":2206898,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T20:39:33.000Z","msg":"紫外線從來都是可免則免，而購買薯仔則是多多益善。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SorNTzE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSorNTzE.jpg&h=df17db87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在大多數的情況下，陽光是我們接觸紫外線的最主要源頭。<br />\n<br />\n太陽放出的紫外線根據波段可分為兩種，UVA和UVB。<br />\n概要來說，UVA(320&ndash;400nm)會曬黑皮膚及引起皺紋，而UVB(280&ndash;320 nm)則會曬傷及曬紅皮膚。<br />\n<br />\n根據世衛所訂下的方式，UV指數的計法是將總紫外線的能量除以25。<br />\n指數高於6表示有高度曬傷風險，而高於11更會對人體構成危險。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SO2hwmn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSO2hwmn.jpg&h=faf48b7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）現今智能手錶、智能眼鏡等設備已逐漸普遍，有不少更設有光觸媒二氧化鈦(TiO2)等物料可以將紫外光量化成電流，然後再根據的電流強弱判斷出紫外線指數。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）近日，有科學家研發出隨著紫外光強弱而變色的麻料（Ref1)，基於毛線表面凹凸不平，因而增加紫外光在裡頭多重折射的機會，變相使在感測方面比普遍的平面光觸媒更為靈敏。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QHK7TzL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQHK7TzL.jpg&h=e3d4294f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他們在文中展示出，改變原材料的做法，可達至不同效果，例如WIFI圖案展示出紫外線的強弱。<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）他們更成功製作出隨紫外光強弱而變色的麻繩，據稱布料彈性十足穿著上非常舒適，而且製作方法可套用在任何製衣物料上。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y3UzyzP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY3UzyzP.jpg&h=e4f23250&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在文中，他們發揮了自己的小宇宙，縫出提子圖案，提子葉加上孔雀石綠感測pH，而提子則由紫外光織成麻繩用作感測UV之用。<br />\n<br />\n無疑，一場時裝界的科學大戰號角已徐徐奏起。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOH4fze6eI6Am6%2FUgKT%2BdzFE%3D&h=0f3dc0bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOH4fze6eI6Am6%2FUgKT%2BdzFE%3D&h=4b3981c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/full/10.1002/admt.202000564\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1002%2Fadmt.202000564&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOH4fze6eI6Am6%2FUgKT%2BdzFE%3D&h=885e4e6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/full/10.1002/admt.202000564</a><br />\n<br />\n明日會停一日更，想花時間在講故台寫文。<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f3fa38c434868a88595e99ec2ff84d94041f41","tid":2206898,"uid":171561,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T20:41:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1030f536db53a643583a697761399e5cca72f45","tid":2206898,"uid":270307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T20:52:13.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"88cac8f45a24d0b2ac4ce1fe6a